"entry finder>`."

#: ../../whatsnew/3.3.rst:2400
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
":mod:`pkgutil` has been converted to use :mod:`importlib` internally. This "
"eliminates many edge cases where the old behaviour of the :pep:`302` import "
